"description" = "Landelela amaphuzu ezinhliziyo ngokushesha futhi kalula!\n\nIlungele wonke umuntu othanda ukudlala Izinhliziyo, noma ngabe ugcina amaphuzu obusuku begeyimu esheshayo noma umdlalo wokuncintisana.\n\nIzici:\n• Isekela abadlali abangu-3–6\n• Umlando ogcwele wegeyimu ukuze ubuyekeze yonke imizuliswano\n• Inkomba yendlela yokudlula – kwesokunxele, kwesokudla, noma bambelela!\n• Inkinobho yokwengeza ngokushesha ukuze unikeze umdlali amaphuzu asele\n• Ukuvumelanisa kwe-iCloud - qala umdlalo ku-iPhone yakho futhi uqhubeke ku-iPad yakho\n• Nyakazisa ukuze uhlehlise umzuliswano odlule\n• Imithetho ye-Flexible Shoot the Moon – susa amaphuzu angu-26 kumdubuli noma wengeze amaphuzu angu-26 kumaphuzu awo wonke umuntu\n• Idizayini ehlanzekile, elula ebukeka iyinhle ngokuma ngobude noma ngokuma kwezwe\n• Usekelo lwemodi emnyama\n\nLolu hlelo lokusebenza lumahhala, umthombo ovulekile, futhi ngeke lufake phakathi izikhangiso.\n\nNgithemba ukuthi uzowujabulela umdlalo wakho olandelayo wezinhliziyo!";
